{
  "id": "cyberpunk-holocard",
  "name": "全息数据卡",
  "category": "cyberpunk",
  "description": "一张赛博朋克风格的全息数据卡，带有霓虹灯效果和故障艺术",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.02,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "赛博|未来|科幻|霓虹|黑客|2077",
        "description": "赛博朋克场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "cardId": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "卡片ID编号"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "卡片标题"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发送者名称"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "接收者名称"
    },
    "senderCode": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发送者代号"
    },
    "priority": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "HIGH",
      "options": ["LOW", "MEDIUM", "HIGH", "CRITICAL"],
      "description": "优先级"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "消息内容"
    },
    "timestamp": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "时间戳"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一张全息数据卡的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 发送者：{{sender}}\n- 接收者：{{recipient}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容要有科技感和未来感\n2. 可以包含加密信息或任务指令\n3. 语气要符合赛博朋克风格\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n\n请直接输出内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "cyberpunk",
    "colors": ["#0ff", "#f0f", "#0a0a0f"],
    "mood": "科技未来"
  },
  "rarity": "rare",
  "collectible": true
}